Class ReportScreen

java.lang.Object
controller.ReportScreen
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ReportScreen extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Controller class that shows the customer various reports. Shows the user the number of appointments per month and type. Shows the user the number of customers per division. Shows the user the appointment schedule for all contacts.
